title: [LucarioPK Subs] Pokemon XY 03 [English Sub]
description:
After finally registering for the Kalos League, Satoshi and friends embark on a new journey. The first stop is Hakudan (Santalune) City. On their way, they encounter a precarious Yayakoma who causes a bit of trouble, yet is very skilled. What must Satoshi and Keromatsu do to teach Yayakoma the error of its ways?
